data.title: HSJ shortlist for 'Provider of the Year' :: Central London Community Healthcare NHS Trust
data.meta_description: We're delighted to be named in the shortlist for the Provider of the Year category in this year's Health Service Journal Awards.
data.text:
We're delighted to be named in the shortlist for the Provider of the Year category in this year's Health Service Journal Awards. The shortlists across all 23 categories have been announced today, with final judging still to come in October.

Winners will be announced on 22 November. There's been a huge response to the awards this year with more than 1500 entries. HSJ editor Alastair McLellan said: "Competition to be shortlisted has once again been fierce. Congratulations to all that have made the grade."
